support 320px -> max-width

viewport meta tag: <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

natural responsiveness

rem
max-width
avoid fixed width and height
avoid heights altogether: prefer using margina + padding
appropriate for fixed widths: 32px icon etc, 250px sidebar
use static margin instead of %

grid: grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr))
Responsive Holy Grail Layout with Grid
flex: flex-wrap

calc()
min()
max()
clamp()

responsive images:
  background-size, background-position -> body { background-image: url(); background-size: cover;}
  object-fit -> img { object-fit: cover; }
  <picture>

media queries:
  body {
    margin: 24px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    body {
      margin: 8px;
    }
  }
